Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.99,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Vamos a salir a buscarlas, muchacho!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.93,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Yokai henge mo buttobashi{\i0}
